<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>手记 · Macintosh 手记</title><link>https://example.com/notes/</link><description>碎念与短记。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Aug 1997 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.com/notes/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>白金，不是米色</title><link>https://example.com/notes/platinum-not-beige/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Aug 1997 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/notes/platinum-not-beige/</guid><category>碎念</category><description>&lt;p&gt;有人看了一眼说：&amp;ldquo;又是个米黄色老电脑。&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不。9600 的机箱是&lt;strong&gt;白金色&lt;/strong&gt;（Platinum），冷调的浅灰带一点点蓝绿，是苹果 1987 年之后统一的配色。米色（beige）是更早的 Macintosh Plus、SE 那一代，暖调发黄。两者差一个时代。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>顶部那条菜单栏</title><link>https://example.com/notes/menu-bar/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 Aug 1997 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/notes/menu-bar/</guid><category>碎念</category><description>&lt;p&gt;现在的软件把菜单藏进汉堡包、藏进右键、藏进&amp;quot;更多&amp;quot;。当年不是这样——菜单栏永远在屏幕最顶上那一条，全局唯一，谁在前台就显谁的菜单。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>关于“慢”这件事</title><link>https://example.com/notes/on-slowness/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 1997 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/notes/on-slowness/</guid><category>手记</category><description>&lt;p&gt;软盘读一秒，窗口开一下，都要等。等待不总是坏事——它给动作留了重量。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>键盘声音收藏</title><link>https://example.com/notes/keyboard-sounds/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 1997 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://example.com/notes/keyboard-sounds/</guid><category>手记</category><description>&lt;p&gt;在收集不同机械键盘的落键声。目前最爱的是 Apple Extended Keyboard II 的那记闷响。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>